<font color="#FF0000">REPLY TO JOHN RATLIFF ET AL</font><br>
<tt>Tue Sep 16 22:24:15 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
John Ratliff, I hate to see you go, but I understand why.It is called the Hyena Pack Syndrome, and unfortunately, it is trying to take over what was &quot;our site&quot;.  Please don't leave, stand and fight the &quot;barbarians at the gate&quot;. I.E. don't leave.<br><br>
Cook and I have at least learned to keep to our own sides of the lake. That is something at least equal to Bibi and Arafat learning how to talk to each other. Trust each other? Never.<br><br>
I too yearn for the likes of DocDel or ClassLass, and am saddened by the rude treatment of VietSon, but this &quot;new&quot; site of followers must be understood. Perhaps this is a cyber phenonomen, but I think, sadly, it is typical of American Society as a whole.  The lowest common demoninator seems to seek its own and spread like the Ebola Virus.<br><br>
This still is a place of serious discussion, in depth exploration of feelings, of weighing of consequences, of past reflections, regardless of how the later day rambo's want to make it their very own clubhouse.  Please do not let that happen.  Your input, often very critical of me, (ouch) was well thought out and often painfully accurate.  You are needed to continue with it.<br><br>
The baloney hero worship that I have seen on this site lately sicken's me, from secret language to respect because someone wanted to be a politician, (Jesus, a politician? Are they not the scum of society?), and now we have the group think, the group attack, the group surpress, to anything that challenges their group mentality).  Sort of like the brownshirt mentality of the last great war, isn't it?  So, to John, DocDel, Tanker, Sarg, ClassLass, Viet Son, Chet, and many others, who I hope are still reading, please get re-involved. Challenge the group think mentality.<br><br>
The future of this site is bigger then the hyena pack, but if you all bail out, then they win by default.  &quot;We&quot;, actually you guys, lost Viet Nam, (or our so called leaders sold them and you out), let us not lose this site too.
<p><code>-- Shrink4u@mail.quik.com  (Doc Spatz) </code><p>


